_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Speaking toi\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1063}, {\"ngram\": \"the luxury travel specialist atScott Dunn\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympics\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1184}, {\"ngram\": \"the option\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I pre-registered to buy tickets and was given access in one of the later purchase windows, on 17 May 2023.\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1374, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1299}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"the later purchase windows\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"17 May\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At that time, I bought the basketball tickets in Lille and the canoe slalom ones.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1426, \"end\": 1431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9996064361120441, \"rank\": 0.0003937187815608545, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1389}, {\"ngram\": \"the basketball tickets\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the canoe slalom ones\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in November, further tickets were suddenly available, which is when we were able to secure the men's artistic gymnastics finals tickets.\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1601, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"November\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1476}, {\"ngram\": \"further tickets\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's artistic gymnastics finals tickets\", \"from\": 1556, \"to\": 1600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was wonderful, but also incredibly annoying as I would never have bought the canoe slalom tickets if I had felt that I had better options, in my opinion.\\\"\", \"from\": 1602, \"to\": 1761, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the canoe slalom tickets\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1704}, {\"ngram\": \"better options\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1744}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The tickets set them back by \\u00a31,770.11 for the three of them - over a third of their overall spend.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The tickets\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"a third\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1838}, {\"ngram\": \"their overall spend\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The family arrived by Eurostar on Saturday 27 July, tickets which cost a total of \\u00a3321 with the Lille station fortunately only a short walk from their aparthotel in the city.\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1886, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0338976413351852e-18, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9996064361120441, \"rank\": 0.0003937187815608545, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The family\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"a total\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1942}, {\"ngram\": \"only a short walk\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2003}, {\"ngram\": \"their aparthotel\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2025}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 2029, \"to\": 2037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their one-bedroom apartment with a kitchen and washing machine cost \\u00a3809.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their one-bedroom apartment\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2066}, {\"ngram\": \"a kitchen and washing machine cost\", \"from\": 2072, \"to\": 2106}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During their time in Lille, outside of watching the Games they enjoyed dinner out every day but one - when they cooked in the apartment - costing around \\u00a370 per meal.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2135, \"end\": 2140, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9996064361120441, \"rank\": 0.0003937187815608545, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their time\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2171}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2191}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartment\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2249}, {\"ngram\": \"meal\", \"from\": 2275, \"to\": 2279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Light lunches and snacks on their way to the stadium cost around \\u00a325 per day.\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Light lunches\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2294}, {\"ngram\": \"snacks\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"their way\", \"from\": 2309, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium cost\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2338}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2357}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One day, as a treat while watching the basketball, the hotdogs, arancini and chips at the Stade Pierre-Mauroy cost \\u00a321 roughly.\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2486, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One day\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"a treat\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2378}, {\"ngram\": \"the basketball\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The trio took a train from Lille to Paris on Tuesday 30 July, costing \\u00a3105.08, where they were staying for two more nights.\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"score\": 0.9996064361120441, \"rank\": 0.0003937187815608545, \"text\": \"Lille\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lille\"}, {\"begin\": 2524, \"end\": 2529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.271994747370809e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The trio\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2496}, {\"ngram\": \"a train\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 2544, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"two more nights\", \"from\": 2595, \"to\": 2610}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here, they stayed in a four-star hotel for \\u00a3714.\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a four-star hotel\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2650}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As they were just moments from the Eiffel Tower, one night they decided to take a trip to the top for a meal.\", \"from\": 2662, \"to\": 2771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just moments\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"a trip\", \"from\": 2742, \"to\": 2748}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"a meal\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All in, this cost \\u00a3125.12 including tickets for the lift, a pizza to share, drinks and some memorabilia.\", \"from\