y\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3615}, {\"ngram\": \"3 August\", \"from\": 3616, \"to\": 3624}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 3650, \"to\": 3657}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3675}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3682}, {\"ngram\": \"the Rugby\", \"from\": 3701, \"to\": 3710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was only there for about 24 hours because I found a cheap British Airways flight home the next day for \\u00a337, which was a lot less than the \\u00a3189 I paid for the Eurostar from London.\\\"\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3874, \"end\": 3882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0338976413351852e-18, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 3888, \"end\": 3894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7358525132797327e-20, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"about 24 hours\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deepak wanted to keep costs as low as possible, so kept meals very low-key.\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3973, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Deepak\", \"from\": 3898, \"to\": 3904}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3925}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3959}, {\"ngram\": \"very low-key\", \"from\": 3960, \"to\": 3972}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He spent \\u00a34.50 on breakfast on the Eurostar, \\u00a33.50 on a sandwich from M&S in King's Cross station which he ate for lunch, and \\u00a318 on dinner in a local French restaurant.\", \"from\": 3974, \"to\": 4143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4009, \"end\": 4017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0338976413351852e-18, \"text\": \"Eurostar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eurostar\"}, {\"begin\": 4044, \"end\": 4047, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marks_&_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9993870436348763, \"rank\": 0.0006133323111127013, \"text\": \"M&S\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marks_&_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marks_&_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 4051, \"end\": 4055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"score\": 0.9998110493675473, \"rank\": 0.00016110812970932374, \"text\": \"King\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/King\"}, {\"begin\": 4125, \"end\": 4131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.8759277092559037, \"rank\": 0.14163511003983933, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakfast\", \"from\": 3992, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"a sandwich\", \"from\": 4028, \"to\": 4038}, {\"ngram\": \"lunch\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4094}, {\"ngram\": \"dinner\", \"from\": 4107, \"to\": 4113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only other times he dipped into his pocket was for a \\u00a31.50 bottle of water, a \\u00a31.81 trip on the Metro in Paris and \\u00a35.99, before the trip, on a few Fiji flags from Amazon.\", \"from\": 4145, \"to\": 4320, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4254, \"end\": 4259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.271994747370809e-22, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4297, \"