/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 4873, \"end\": 4879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esau\", \"score\": 0.9993298851635082, \"rank\": 0.0006646469562100973, \"text\": \"Judith\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Esau\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Two adults\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4803}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 4805, \"to\": 4817}, {\"ngram\": \"seven nights\", \"from\": 4822, \"to\": 4834}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 4904, \"to\": 4915}, {\"ngram\": \"Jesper\", \"from\": 4916, \"to\": 4922}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'Category A' package\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 4975}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 4979, \"to\": 4986}, {\"ngram\": \"February\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 4998}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This included access to the men's gymnastics qualifiers - \\u00a3112 each, the men's and women's archery - \\u00a343 each, and the women's volleyball prelims - \\u00a3103 each.\", \"from\": 5011, \"to\": 5169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5031}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's gymnastics qualifiers\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5066}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's and women's archery\", \"from\": 5080, \"to\": 5109}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's volleyball prelims\", \"from\": 5126, \"to\": 5156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The couple spent \\u00a356 roughly to get from their house in Langdon Hills, Essex, to London St Pancras, before hopping on the Eurostar which they booked in November last year and cost them \\u00a3476 for a return ticket.\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5227, \"end\": 5240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langdon_Hills\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Langdon Hills\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langdon_Hills\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Langdon_Hills\"}, 