\"ngram\": \"a larger evening meal\", \"from\": 6041, \"to\": 6062}, {\"ngram\": \"a restaurant\", \"from\": 6066, \"to\": 6078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Our average spend was \\u00a3100 per day for two people on food, including alcohol - usually a couple of beers for my husband and a mocktail or a prosecco for me.\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our average spend\", \"from\": 6080, \"to\": 6097}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 6111, \"to\": 6114}, {\"ngram\": \"two people\", \"from\": 6119, \"to\": 6129}, {\"ngram\": \"food\", \"from\": 6133, \"to\": 6137}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 6149, \"to\": 6156}, {\"ngram\": \"usually a couple\", \"from\": 6159, \"to\": 6175}, {\"ngram\": \"beers\", \"from\": 6179, \"to\": 6184}, {\"ngram\": \"my husband\", \"from\": 6189, \"to\": 6199}, {\"ngram\": \"a mocktail\", \"from\": 6204, \"to\": 6214}, {\"ngram\": \"a prosecco\", \"from\": 6218, \"to\": 6228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Other than that, we spent \\u00a315 per day on refreshments and \\u00a380 on merch.\", \"from\": 6238, \"to\": 6310, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 6273, \"to\": 6276}, {\"ngram\": \"refreshments\", \"from\": 6280, \"to\": 6292}, {\"ngram\": \"merch\", \"from\": 6304, \"to\": 6309}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for me, it was always a dream to visit an Olympic Games so I did not mind spending the money to ensure we enjoyed it.\", \"from\": 6311, \"to\": 6432, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 6337, \"to\": 6344}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic Games\", \"from\": 6354, \"to\": 6370}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 6398, \"to\": 6407}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The experience was well worth the money, in my opinion.\\\"\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6491, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The experience\", \"from\": 6435, \"to\": 6449}, {\"ngram\": \"my opinion\", \"from\": 6479, \"to\": 6489}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate All rights reserved.\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6550, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Impartial news + intelligent debate\", \"from\": 6493, \"to\": 6528}, {\"ngram\": \"All rights\", \"from\": 6529, \"to\": 6539}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00a9 2026 Associated Newspapers Limited.\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00a9\", \"from\": 6551, \"to\": 6552}]}]}"